==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smarten
<hw>Smart"en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make smart or
spruce; -- usually with <xex>up</xex>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>She had to go and <qex>smarten</qex> herself up somewhat.</q>
<rj><qau>W. Black.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smartle</ent>⟦br⟧
